* Iris sighed as she scenned Prowls spark speed up.*

IRIS: " Calm! Featherhead! If your spark beat's too fast it'll wrech the 
settings!"

* Iron Raptor growled as she turned her head a bit towards her back and 
towards Iris.*

" Lay off, Iris! He's trying."

* With that she simply turned her head back towards the direction where they 
were going, picking up her speed.
Iris sighed, if she could have made a face towards Iron she would have.

Iron Raptor could feel Prowl lean forward and rest on her a bit, liking the 
feeling but a little tense about all this herself.

Iris swears as Prowl nearly drops the screen.*
" You dolt! Careful! Without me you'll both die!"
